 Edit an Output Node in a Batch Data Transform

To ensure accuracy and data uniqueness, generate a UUID for each row in a table to maintain distinct values. As you combine data from various sources within a batch data transform, you can potentially duplicate or overwrite rows that contain similar ID values.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

When: This feature is available starting in June 2024.
title: Enhance Row Security in Batch Data Transforms
